Happy Holidays & Christmas to all our friends around the world. May this year & next be filled with Love, Health, Joy & Magic. Thank you for the positive vibes you bring to this community. 2023 will be one of the most yearly years yet!☃️❄️🎉 
  Ava (@miiumaux), amazing to remember it’s been Almost 10 Christmas’s with You & I couldn’t be more grateful. Thank you for the Love, Kindness & Inspiration you bring to me & the world! I love you, happy holidays.❤️❄️ #holiday

Starting 2023 by working on some of the coolest Animated & Musical projects of my career so far! ✨As a Latino American, getting the chance to voice characters I connect with, is a dream come true. 🎶
Photos:@miiumaux 
Studio: @dallasaudiopost 
Gear: @neumann.berlin 
for making such great equipment! 

#voiceover #acting #behindthescenes #animation #sound

Animation is an art, medium & community that always strives to push the entertainment envelope forward.✨ Giving heart & truth to an imagination makes it, a Real Experience.  Thank you to all of the mentors & people whom over the years, have shared a bit of their Light, Love, Kindness, Knowledge & Expertise, with This “Forever Student of Life” (Ya know who you are.) 
  My journey leads me here & I will respect every step I have walked along this path. May we all continue moving forward together.⚡️✌️✨I am lucky to be creating awesome things with amazing people.✨🎙️
